data.description: Welcome to 133 Oak Drive, a stunning 3-story haven nestled in the esteemed Stone Brook subdivision. This 4-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom residence boasts an array of luxurious features to elevate your lifestyle. Step inside to discover exquisite bamboo wood flooring, plush carpeting, and elegant tile accents throughout. The bathrooms beckon a walk-in shower, and double vanity sink. While the master has a walk in closet. The open-concept kitchen and living area, adorned with granite countertops and a deep sink, create the perfect ambiance for entertaining guests. Stay comfortable year-round with two A/C units and cozy up by the gas log fireplace on chilly evenings. The finished basement provides additional living space, while outside, a tranquil creek sets the scene for relaxation, complemented by a rejuvenating hot tub and a 12x28 wired workshop. With a propane tank, 2-car garage, and proximity to excellent schools, this 3078-square-foot sanctuary embodies both elegance and convenience. Experience unparalleled living at 133 Oak Drive.
